quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,"Yemwe bantu! Nimutinye Nyagasani wanyu! Mu by’ukuri, umutingito wo ku munsi w’imperuka ni ikintu gihambaye"
  22,2,"Umunsi muzawubona, buri wese wonsa azibagirwa uwo yonsaga, ndetse na buri wese utwite azakuramo inda. Uzanabona abantu babaye abasinzi kandi atari bo, kubera ko ibihano bya Allah bizaba bikomeye"
  22,3,"No mu bantu hari abajya impaka kuri Allah nta bumenyi babifitiye, bakanakurikira buri shitani ryigometse"
  22,4,"(Iryo shitani) ryaciriweho iteka ko uzarigira inshuti magara rizamuyobya, rikazanamuganisha mu muriro ugurumana"
  22,5,"Yemwe bantu! Niba mushidikanya ko izuka rizabaho (nimutekereze uko twabaremye): mu by’ukuri, twabaremye tubakomoye mu gitaka (umukurambere wanyu Adamu), hanyuma (mwe tubarema) mu ntanga, hanyuma (zihinduka) urusoro rw’amaraso, hanyuma (zihinduka) ikinyama kigaragaza ishusho n’ikitayigaragaza; kugira ngo tubagaragarize (ubushobozi bwacu). Tunarekera muri nyababyeyi uwo dushaka kugeza ku gihe cyagenwe, maze tukabasohora (muri nyababyeyi) muri impinja, (tukabakuza) kugira ngo muzagere mu gihe cyanyu cy’ubukure. No muri mwe, hari abapfa batarageza icyo gihe (cy’ubukure), ndetse no muri mwe hari n’abageramu zabukuru bakamera nk’ahobatigeze bagira icyo bamenya. Ndetse ubona ubutaka bwumaganye, maze twabumanuraho amazi (imvura) bukanyeganyega bukanarumbuka, bukanameraho ibimera binyuranye bishimishije"
  22,6,"Ibyo ni ibigaragaza ko Allah ari ukuri, kandi ko ari we uha ubuzima ibyapfuye, ndetse ko ari weushobora byose"
  22,7,"Kandi ko imperuka izaza nta gushidikanya, ndetse ko Allah azazura abari mu mva"
  22,8,"No mu bantu hari ujya impaka ku byerekeye Allah nta bumenyi (abifitiye), nta muyoboro ndetse nta n’igitabo kimumurikira (afite)"
  22,9,"(Uwo muntu ujya impaka) anaga ijosi (kubera kwibona) kugira ngo ayobye (abantu) inzira ya Allah; azagira ikimwaro ku isi, ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka tuzamusogongeza ibihano by’umuriro utwika"
  22,10,"(Azabwirwa ati) \"Ibyo ni ukubera ibyakozwe n’amaboko yawe, kandi mu by’ukuri, Allahntarenganya abagaragu be"
  22,11,"Ndetse no mu bantu hari ugaragira Allah ashidikanya. Iyo icyiza kimugezeho aratuza, naho yagerwaho n’ikigeragezo agasubira mu buhakanyi (nyuma y’uko yari yarayobotse); ubwo akaba ahombye (ibyiza byo ku) isi n’imperuka. Icyo ni cyo gihombo kigaragara"
  22,12,Asenga ibitari Allahbitagira icyo bimutwara cyangwa ngo bigire icyo bimumarira. Uko ni ko kuyoba guhambaye (kutagira igaruriro)
  22,13,"Asenga icyo inabi yacyo iri hafi kurusha ineza yacyo, kandi rwose (ibyo bihitiyemo gusenga bitari Allah)ni byo barinzi babi ndetse bikaba n’inshuti mbi"
  22,14,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza, Allahazabinjiza mu busitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), kuko rwose Allah akora ibyo ashatse"
  22,15,"Uwo ariwe wese wibwira ko Allah atazatabara (Intumwa Muhamadi) kuri iyi si ndetse no ku munsi w’imperuka,namanike umugozi ku gisenge maze awushyire mu ijosi, narangiza awuce (yiyahure) maze arebe ko umugambi we ukuraho uburakari bwe"
  22,16,"Uko ni nako twahishuye imirongo isobanutse (igitabo cya Qur’an), kandi Allah ayobora uwo ashatse"
  22,17,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bemeye (Allah n’intumwa ye Muhamadi), Abayahudi (abemeye ubutumwa bwa Musa ku gihe cye), Abaswaabi’i (abagumye kuri kamere yabo batagize idini bayoboka), Abakirisitu [abemeye ubutumwa bwa Isa (Yesu) ku gihe cye], Abamajusi (abasenga umuriro) ndetse n’abasenga ibindi bitari Allah; rwose Allah azabakiranura ku munsi w’imperuka. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Umuhamyauhebuje wa buri kintu"
  22,18,"Ese ntubona ko ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi, izuba, ukwezi, inyenyeri, imisozi, ibiti, ibiremwa byose bigenda ku isi ndetse na benshi mu bantubyubamira Allah? Ariko abenshi (mu bantu) bakwiye ibihano. Kandi uwo Allah yasuzuguje ntawamwubaha, kuko mu by’ukuri Allah akora ibyo ashatse"